# CIMP Portal Implementation Checklist

Complete checklist for implementing, deploying, and maintaining the CIMP Portal integrated IDE.

## ✅ Phase 1: Development Setup (Week 1)

### Prerequisites
- [ ] Install .NET 7.0 SDK
- [ ] Install PostgreSQL 15
- [ ] Install Docker & Docker Desktop
- [ ] Install Git
- [ ] Clone repository
- [ ] Review project structure

### Local Environment
- [ ] Read SETUP_GUIDE.md
- [ ] Create PostgreSQL database
- [ ] Create appsettings.Local.json
- [ ] Install .NET dependencies: `dotnet restore`
- [ ] Verify build: `dotnet build`
- [ ] Create database migrations: `dotnet ef database update`
- [ ] Seed test data (optional)
- [ ] Start application: `dotnet run`
- [ ] Access Swagger: http://localhost:5001/swagger

### Basic Testing
- [ ] POST /api/auth/login (with test credentials)
- [ ] GET /api/auth/me
- [ ] Health check: /health
- [ ] Verify database created (8 tables)
- [ ] Check logs (console output)

### Documentation Review
- [ ] Read README.md
- [ ] Read API_REFERENCE.md
- [ ] Read DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md
- [ ] Understand architecture
- [ ] Understand database schema

