- [ ] Verify file operations work correctly

### Execution Endpoints
- [ ] Test POST /api/ide/session/{id}/execute (Python)
- [ ] Test POST /api/ide/session/{id}/execute (Node.js)
- [ ] Test POST /api/ide/session/{id}/execute (Maven)
- [ ] Test GET /api/ide/execution/{id}
- [ ] Test timeout handling (5 minutes)
- [ ] Verify Docker container cleanup
- [ ] Test multiple concurrent executions
- [ ] Verify exit codes captured

### Validation Endpoints
- [ ] Test POST /api/validation/submit
- [ ] Test GET /api/validation/{id}
- [ ] Verify validation status transitions
- [ ] Check JSONB field population

### Error Handling
- [ ] Test 400 Bad Request (invalid input)
- [ ] Test 401 Unauthorized (missing token)
- [ ] Test 403 Forbidden (insufficient permissions)
